---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<Layout>
	<main class="min-h-screen text-slate-950 pb-24" style="background-color: var(--color-bg)">
		<section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 sm:py-16">
			<a href={`${base}/`} class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-6 text-sm text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors text-[0.875rem]" style="font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/></svg>
				Back to home
			</a>
			<div class="rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 sm:p-10 shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/5">
				<h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950 sm:text-5xl">Cookie Policy</h1>
				<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: June 2026</p>

				<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">1. Introduction</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					This Cookie Policy explains how Voyaflair ("we", "our", or "us") uses cookies and similar technologies when you
					visit our website.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					By continuing to browse or use our website, you agree to the use of cookies as described in this Policy,
					subject to your cookie preferences and applicable laws.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">2. What Are Cookies?</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device when you visit a website.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Cookies help websites function properly, improve user experience, remember preferences, analyze website
					performance, and support marketing and advertising activities.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Cookies do not typically contain information that directly identifies a user, but they may be linked to
					information stored about you.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">3. Why We Use Cookies</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">We use cookies for several purposes, including:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Ensuring website functionality</li>
					<li>Improving website performance</li>
					<li>Remembering user preferences</li>
					<li>Understanding visitor behavior</li>
					<li>Measuring website traffic</li>
					<li>Supporting newsletter subscriptions</li>
					<li>Improving content and user experience</li>
					<li>Supporting affiliate partnerships</li>
					<li>Supporting advertising and marketing activities</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">4. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
				<h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Essential Cookies</h3>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">They may include cookies that:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Maintain security</li>
					<li>Prevent abuse and fraud</li>
					<li>Remember cookie preferences</li>
					<li>Support basic website functionality</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Without these cookies, some parts of the website may not function correctly.
				</p>
				<h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Analytics Cookies</h3>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Analytics cookies help us understand how visitors use the website.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">These cookies may collect information such as:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Pages visited</li>
					<li>Time spent on pages</li>
					<li>Device type</li>
					<li>Browser type</li>
					<li>Traffic sources</li>
					<li>General geographic region</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">This information helps us improve our content and user experience.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Analytics tools may include:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Google Analytics</li>
					<li>Other website analytics platforms</li>
				</ul>
				<h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Functional Cookies</h3>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					These cookies remember choices you make and help personalize your experience.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Examples may include:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Language preferences</li>
					<li>Saved settings</li>
					<li>User interface preferences</li>
				</ul>
				<h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Advertising Cookies</h3>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Advertising cookies may be used to deliver relevant advertisements and measure advertising performance.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">These cookies may be set by advertising partners and networks.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					They may track browsing behavior across websites to provide personalized advertising experiences.
				</p>
				<h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Affiliate Tracking Cookies</h3>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Voyaflair may participate in affiliate marketing programs.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Affiliate cookies help track referrals when visitors click affiliate links and make purchases or bookings
					through partner websites.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">These cookies do not increase the cost of any purchase made by visitors.</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">5. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Some cookies may be placed by third-party services integrated into the website.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Examples may include:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Google Analytics</li>
					<li>Email marketing providers</li>
					<li>Advertising networks</li>
					<li>Affiliate platforms</li>
					<li>Embedded content providers</li>
					<li>Social media platforms</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					These third parties may collect information according to their own privacy policies.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Voyaflair does not control the cookies used by third-party services.</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">6. Cookie Consent</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					When required by applicable law, visitors will be presented with a cookie consent banner upon their first
					visit to the website.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Visitors may choose which categories of cookies they wish to accept or reject, except for cookies that are
					strictly necessary for the operation of the website.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Cookie preferences may be updated at any time.</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">7. Managing Cookies</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">Most web browsers allow users to control cookies through browser settings.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Users can:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>View stored cookies</li>
					<li>Delete cookies</li>
					<li>Block cookies</li>
					<li>Receive notifications before cookies are stored</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Please note that disabling certain cookies may affect website functionality and user experience.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">8. Data Collected Through Cookies</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Depending on the type of cookie used, information collected may include:
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>IP address</li>
					<li>Browser information</li>
					<li>Device information</li>
					<li>Operating system</li>
					<li>Referring websites</li>
					<li>Visited pages</li>
					<li>Session information</li>
					<li>General location information</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					This information is generally used for analytical, security, functional, and marketing purposes.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">9. Affiliate Links and Tracking Technologies</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Voyaflair may use affiliate links within articles, guides, newsletters, and other content.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Affiliate partners may use cookies or similar tracking technologies to recognize referrals and attribute
					commissions.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					These technologies help support the operation and maintenance of the website at no additional cost to users.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">10. Advertising Technologies</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Voyaflair may use advertising services that rely on cookies and similar technologies.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">These technologies may be used to:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Display advertisements</li>
					<li>Measure campaign performance</li>
					<li>Improve ad relevance</li>
					<li>Prevent fraud</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Advertising partners may collect information in accordance with their own privacy policies.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">11. Updates to This Cookie Policy</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in technology, legal requirements, or
					website operations.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">The most current version will always be available on this page.</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">12. Contact Information</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					If you have any questions regarding this Cookie Policy, please contact:
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7">
					<a href="mailto:voyaflair@gmail.com" class="font-medium text-slate-900 underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-slate-700 text-[0.875rem]" style="font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;">voyaflair@gmail.com</a>
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<Footer />
</Layout>
